"> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Sightseeing,Events', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Sightseeing,Events"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-DOWNTOWN_0000s_0001_ROVE-DOWNTOWN-21-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Rove Downtown Hotel swimming pool with a view of Dubai skyline" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-DOWNTOWN_0000s_0003_ROVE-DOWNTOWN-02-600x375-1.jpg" alt="View from Rove Downtown Hotel room overlooking Dubai skyline" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-DOWNTOWN_0000s_0000_ROVE-DOWNTOWN-34-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Rove Downtown Hotel interiors featuring modern and cozy design" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-DOWNTOWN_0000s_0002_ROVE-DOWNTOWN-4-2-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Rove Downtown Hotel lobby with modern and welcoming design" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove Downtown</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>Rove Downtown puts you at the doorstep of an unending stream of entertainment, dining and shopping in the city’s most iconic locale, where Burj Khalifa and the Dubai Mall take centre stage.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/downtown/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Seafront', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Seafront"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-LA-MER-BEACH_0000s_0000_V01_POST-copy-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove La Mer Beach Hotel with J1 Beach in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-LA-MER-BEACH-07-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove La Mer Beach Hotel near J1 Beach in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-LA-MER-BEACH_0000s_0003_ROVE-LA-MER-BEACH-eng-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Pool view at Rove La Mer Beach Hotel overlooking J1 Beach" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-LA-MER-BEACH-09-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Lobby view of Rove La Mer Beach Hotel in J1 Beach Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-LA-MER-BEACH_0000s_0002_ROVE-LA-MER-BEACH-08-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Room at Rove La Mer Beach Hotel with a pool view overlooking J1 Beach" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove La Mer Beach</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>Where surf meets city. Soak in sun, sand, and pristine waters, explore trendy boardwalk restaurants, and discover Jumeirah—Dubai's iconic and historic neighbourhood. </p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-la-mer-beach/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Seafront', 'Ras Al Khaimah, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Ras Al Khaimah, UAE" data-tab="Seafront"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ROAM_IMAGES_19808-e1768309319482.jpg" alt="Exterior View of Rove Al Marjan Island Hotel" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Untitled-1000-x-1000-px.jpg" alt="Rove Al Marjan Island - Ras Al Khaimah" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ROAM_WEBSITE_1980_10807-1-e1768309121183.jpg" alt="Rove Al Marjan Hotel - Ras Al Khaimah" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/4.jpg" alt="Rove Al Marjan Lobby" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/17.jpg" alt="Rove Al Marjan Island Pool - Ras Al Khaimah" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19.jpg" alt="Rove Al Marjan Island Restaurant - Ras Al Khaimah" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/25.jpg" alt="Rove Al Marjan Island Exterior - Best Hotel in Ras Al Khaimah" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=5"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=6"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove Al Marjan Island</h6> <div class="city">Ras Al Khaimah, UAE</div> <p>Right on the water in Al Marjan Island—one of the UAE's top destinations. Discover beachfront clubs, dining hotspots, a walkable waterfront, and white sandy beaches.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-al-marjan-island/" class="btn contessa">Know more</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Events', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Events"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-EXPO-2020_0000s_0004_ROVE-EXPO-2020-00-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove Expo City enterance to Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-EXPO-2020_0000s_0003_ROVE-EXPO-2020-01-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove Expo City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-EXPO-2020_0000s_0002_ROVE-EXPO-2020-20-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Rove Expo Hotel in Dubai with an outside view of Expo City" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-EXPO-2020_0000s_0001_ROVE-EXPO-2020-21-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Rove Expo Hotel in Dubai with The Daily Restaurant" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-EXPO-2020_0000s_0000_ROVE-EXPO-2020-26-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Gaming area at Rove Expo Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove Expo City</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>Rove Expo City puts you in futuristic Expo City Dubai. Walk to Dubai Exhibition Centre, steps from Dubai Metro, and minutes from DWC Airport and Dubai Marina</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-expo-2020/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Sightseeing,Events', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Sightseeing,Events"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-WALK_0000s_0002_ROVE-CITY-WALK-1-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove City Walk Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-WALK_0000s_0000_ROVE-CITY-WALK-19-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove Expo City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-WALK_0006_ROVE-CITY-WALK-4-2-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Lobby of Rove City Walk Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-WALK_0004_ROVE-CITY-WALK-4-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Lobby area of Rove City Walk Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-WALK_0005_ROVE-CITY-WALK-4-4-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Music area near Rove City Walk Hotel and Coca-Cola Arena in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove City Walk</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>Your stylish retreat in Dubai’s trendiest neighborhood. Enjoy boutique shopping, global dining, and easy urban exploration. Just 5 minutes from Dubai Mall with direct access to the city’s main highway.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-city-walk/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Sightseeing', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Sightseeing"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0000_ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY-25-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove Healthcare City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/08-Rove-Healthcare-city-hotel--scaled.jpg" alt="New Rover Plus Room at Rove Healthcare city hotel -" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/10-Rove-Healthcare-city-hotel-scaled.jpg" alt="New Rover Plus Room at Rove Healthcare city hotel -" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY-07-1-1-1-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Lobby of Rove Healthcare City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0001_ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY-10-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Swimming pool view at Rove Healthcare City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0002_ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY-08-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Room with outside view at Rove Healthcare City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0003_ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY-05-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Gaming area at Rove Healthcare City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=5"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=6"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove Bur Dubai</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>Best of both business and leisure at Rove Bur Dubai - Healthcare City. This hyper-connected location puts key business hubs, entertainment, and leisure destinations within 10 minutes' drive.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-healthcare-city-bur-dubai/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Events', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Events"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-TRADE-CENTRE-11-min-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Night exterior view of Rove Trade Centre Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-TRADE-CENTRE-08-min-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Waiting area at Rove Trade Centre Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-TRADE-CENTRE_0000s_0000_ROVE-TRADE-CENTRE-09-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Swimming pool at Rove Trade Centre Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-TRADE-CENTRE-26-min-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Indoor games area at Rove Trade Centre Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-TRADE-CENTRE-03-min-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Meeting room at Rove Trade Centre Hotel for business events" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove Trade Centre</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>At Dubai World Trade Centre and 10 minutes from Downtown Dubai and City Walk, Rove Trade Centre is perfect for work, play, and urban exploration—right at the edge between new and old Dubai.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-trade-centre/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Theme-Parks', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Theme-Parks"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1520x586-6-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Room interior view at Rove at the Park Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-AT-THE-PARK_0000s_0003_ROVE-AT-THE-PARK-19-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Front office area view of Rove at the Park Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-AT-THE-PARK_0000s_0002_ROVE-AT-THE-PARK-21-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Pool area at Rove at the Park Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-AT-THE-PARK_0000s_0001_ROVE-AT-THE-PARK-25-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Indoor gaming area at Rove at the Park Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove at the Park</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>Your perfect base for Dubai Parks & Resorts adventures, with theme parks, waterpark fun, and cozy comfort. Business hubs are just minutes away.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-dubai-parks-resorts-jebel-ali/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Sightseeing,Seafront', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Sightseeing,Seafront"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0001_Rove_V01-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Lobby area at Rove Dubai Marina Hotel" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0002_ROVE-DUBAI-MARINA-29-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove Healthcare City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0003_ROVE-DUBAI-MARINA-17-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Lobby area of Rove Healthcare City Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0000_Rove_V07-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Swimming pool view at Rove Hotels" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-HEALTHCARE-CITY_0000s_0004_ROVE-DUBAI-MARINA-05-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Outside view from Rove Hotel rooms in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove Dubai Marina</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>The perfect launchpad for thrill or chill—our Dubai Marina hotel serves art enthusiasts and beach lovers, shopaholics and adrenaline junkies alike. It's the ideal spot to explore Dubai's true diversity.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-dubai-marina/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Sightseeing', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Sightseeing"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-CENTRE_0000s_0001_ROVE-CITY-CENTRE-20-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Rove City Centre Hotel lobby with modern and comfortable design" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-CENTRE_0000s_0004_ROVE-CITY-CENTRE-02-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Rove City Centre Hotel lobby with modern and comfortable design" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-CENTRE-10-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Room view at Rove City Centre Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-CENTRE_0000s_0003_ROVE-CITY-CENTRE-05-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Exterior view of Rove City Centre Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ROVE-CITY-CENTRE_0000s_0000_ROVE-CITY-CENTRE-32-600x375-1.jpg" alt="Places near Rove City Centre Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove City Centre, Deira</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>Experience Dubai’s maritime heritage at the heart of the city. The perfect base for Dubai Creek, souks, and cafés. Only 10 minutes from Dubai International Airport and near Dubai Metro.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-city-centre-deira-dubai/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="hotel" :class="{'active': isHotelActive('Sightseeing,Seafront', 'Dubai, UAE')}" data-dropdown="Dubai, UAE" data-tab="Sightseeing,Seafront"> <div class="inner-wrapper" x-data="{'show': 'gallery'}" :class="show"> <div class="media"> <div class="media-switch"> <a @click.prevent="show='gallery'" class="show-gallery">Show Gallery</a> </div> <div class="slider"> <div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"> <div class="glide__slides"> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Rove_JBR_Map.jpg" alt="Rove JBR Beach Hotel Dubai | Hotels in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Rove_JBR_15-scaled.jpg" alt="Rove JBR Beach Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Rove_JBR_06-scaled.jpg" alt="Rove JBR Beach Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Rove_JBR_07-scaled.jpg" alt="Rove JBR Beach Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Rove_JBR_05-scaled.jpg" alt="Rove JBR Beach Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> <div class="glide__slide"> <div class="img-wrapper"> <img src="https://rovem.beetlecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Rove_JBR_04-scaled.jpg" alt="Rove JBR Beach Hotel in Dubai" class="img"> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="glide__bullets" data-glide-el="controls[nav]"> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=0"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=1"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=2"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=3"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=4"></button> <button class="glide__bullet" data-glide-dir="=5"></button> </div> </div> </div> <div class="info"> <h6 class="title">Rove JBR</h6> <div class="city">Dubai, UAE</div> <p>The perfect launchpad for beach lovers — our JBR hotel is your gateway to sun, sand, and seaside thrills. From laid-back beach days to buzzing cafés, it's the ideal spot to experience Dubai's coastal charm.</p> <a href="/en/hotels/rove-jbr/" class="btn contessa">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="load-more-wrapper" x-show="showLoadM